#   grids (n x 2) floating 3 cm above tessellated substrates (log-depth
#   z-fight rule), mirrored to both faces with flipped normals. Nadir (-Y)
#   phased-array panel 3 cm below a 3x4-tessellated nadir face; octagon
#   thruster on +Z. Axes: +Y zenith, -Y nadir, +Z anti-velocity, X span.
